00:19:13,600 --> 00:19:14,160
You...

295
00:19:17,140 --> 00:19:17,820
My Lord.

296
00:19:18,480 --> 00:19:19,820
So Miss Zhaoyan

297
00:19:19,820 --> 00:19:21,690
