298
00:19:21,690 --> 00:19:23,460
She knows she's not welcome here,

299
00:19:23,460 --> 00:19:24,850
but still took the risk and came in.

300
00:19:24,850 --> 00:19:25,730
Looks like Miss Zhaoyan

301
00:19:25,730 --> 00:19:28,060
