302
00:19:28,300 --> 00:19:28,930
My Lord.

303
00:19:29,210 --> 00:19:30,650
If she can solve the case

304
00:19:30,770 --> 00:19:32,530
and become your subordinate,

305
00:19:32,650 --> 00:19:35,580
