555
00:36:09,360 --> 00:36:10,930
She's full of nonsense.

556
00:36:11,130 --> 00:36:12,780
Who knows whether she's lying or not?

557
00:36:12,780 --> 00:36:14,350
I won't go.

558
00:36:19,270 --> 00:36:20,030
Zhaoyan.

559
00:36:22,400 --> 00:36:23,750
