561
00:36:25,640 --> 00:36:27,650
I was worried you would be in danger too.

562
00:36:27,650 --> 00:36:29,380
Have you found any clues?

563
00:36:31,280 --> 00:36:32,610
I'm fine.

564
00:36:33,410 --> 00:36:35,770
